column5: Found this on the Cabelas.ca website and am considering buying it.  http://www.cabelas.ca//store/?ID=4494&section=1188  Has anyone ever owned or used one before?  Is it worth it?
Awesome reel, I have a bunch of them. That is a great deal.
My buddy has 2. I used them for a couple outings and they are impressive. That's a good price to.
i have 2, great reels! cant go wrong with it.
good reel for that price.  i just sold my last one as i prefer the feel of the curado, especially the E series.  all personal preference at that level.
At that price it's a good deal.  I have one of them and they are awesome.    Can't wait to try my new Curado 201E though
